Description: An efficient R wrapper for the CISNET Smoking History Generator.
    The package Version field encodes the bundled engine and R wrapper releases
    in the form ENGINE-RWRAPPER (for example 6.5.2-1.0.0). Optional shg-cli sync
    metadata (tag, commit, shared-file hash) lives in src/shg-cli-info.txt (YAML under
    shg-cli:); see tools/shg-sync.py update-description.
